    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is indeed a very complex and interesting use case that we currently don't cover. We've made an example on how to do this kind of use case with React InstantSearch, but not yet with InstantSearch.js. Does the behaviour in https://codesandbox.io/s/kwklo3rz63 describe your use case? You can make something similar to this with InstantSearch.js connectors.\r\n\r\nWhen you are talking about start and end date, do you expect the filtering to be overlapping that date completely, or just including?",
